2. PRIVATE ranges
------------------

The `PRIVATE` tag in `geoip.dat` is built from well-known standard
special-purpose and private address ranges (RFC 1112, RFC 1122, RFC 1918,
RFC 2544, RFC 3068, RFC 3171, RFC 3927, RFC 4193, RFC 4291, RFC 4843,
RFC 5737, RFC 6598, RFC 6890). These ranges are not derived from any
third-party dataset and carry no additional license restrictions.


